    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "gremlins? lol. i mean, i get what you mean with the metaphor but i'm just trying to figure out if this is a technical glitch or something else. i checked the scanner logs too and they seem to match up with the scans they're actually doing. if it's not the people or the scanners, what else could it be?",
